    <item>
      <title>财政部在关税焦虑中恢复了一年的低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/treasury-yields-head-back-toward-year-s-lows-on-tariff-angst</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府债券收益率转移到了一年中的最低水平，因为投资者坚信，贸易引起的增长放缓将导致美联储今年多次降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/treasury-yields-head-back-toward-year-s-lows-on-tariff-angst</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 16:13:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国在2030年以后的石油税计划来替换意外职责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/uk-drafts-post-2030-oil-tax-plan-to-replace-windfall-duties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府正在起草新的税收制度，以供石油和天然气公司在2030年以后替代有争议的意外收获税，目的是只有在价格异常高的情况下才能击中公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/uk-drafts-post-2030-oil-tax-plan-to-replace-windfall-duties</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 15:40:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>官员说，除非所有美国征费都取消，否</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/canada-won-t-scrap-tariffs-unless-all-us-levies-are-lifted-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据加拿大政府高级官员称，如果美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）留下加拿大的任何关税，总理贾斯汀·特鲁多（Justin Trudeau）不​​愿意举起加拿大的全部报复性关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/canada-won-t-scrap-tariffs-unless-all-us-levies-are-lifted-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 15:25:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国的衰老能源网格从支出计划中获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/germany-s-aging-energy-grids-seen-as-winners-from-spending-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国制定5000亿欧元（5340亿美元）的基础设施基金的计划使能源电网有望在经过多年的投资不足之后的巨大支出增长，这是彻底改变该国的公共财务并促进经济发展的更广泛努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/germany-s-aging-energy-grids-seen-as-winners-from-spending-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 13:17:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Andurand的对冲基金在37％的低迷后消除了2024年的增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/andurand-s-hedge-fund-erases-last-year-s-gains-after-37-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[石油交易员皮埃尔·安杜兰（Pierre Andurand）从2025年的前两个月中删除了他的所有收益，继续在波动商品市场上骑车。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/andurand-s-hedge-fund-erases-last-year-s-gains-after-37-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 10:58:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
